:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"叫佢參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(轉)區議會長期作戰計劃: 如何令建制派永不翻身<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756295</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"244d6d78c6ec24f010a5d6096ce404ef447379fc","tid":1756580,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6361f4fbf5b9a20d65259023895142395b4c68","tid":1756580,"uid":16830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"地區野一定要問泛民果邊借個人做助手, 唔係 d 問題根本唔知從何入手, 連去邊個部門都未知<br />\n<br />\n可以叫手足幫手搞掂個 setup, 再同有經驗既泛民助手請教下區議員權限/守則同可用資源(呢d 好難靠普通手足, 時間就係金錢) , 最後就動用資源請手足建立自己班底"},{"pid":"b81e7fdce07a3e5a7d1713ad5c11bdc406a941c6","tid":1756580,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de5f213f89b429c5aa4612e299f5d8f985717b30","tid":1756580,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"唔落手幫都幫手做各行業既顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8762a11c51471527b667cead6840c24d37541a6","tid":1756580,"uid":26908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"真心，素人冇經驗冇人脈，佢地需要人幫，如果唔係好難做到野，起好個頭好緊要，個頭衰咗之後會越做越頹。"},{"pid":"3687ccb979dcf51655a4d1c7b658b337ea08f619","tid":1756580,"uid":62151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">香港仲有230萬人未登記做選民<br />\n<br />\n登記做選民備戰立法會<br />\n<br />\n登記唔洗錢，何樂而不為<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>[香港立法會選舉備戰] 學習美國民主黨如何為2020年總統大選總動員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756444</a></blockquote></span>"},{"pid":"2056809316d7d68cc5acc14a71200ac98ce23d5f","tid":1756580,"uid":26908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:36:15.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"}]}